Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.34,0:00:18.31,Lucy-Song-Title,,0,0,0,,[I want to be a rainbow]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa hoshifuru yoru ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.70,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono tomoshibi wo keshi wa shinai to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wasurenai wa akane no asa ni chikatta kotoba
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.76,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Wakaba ni somaru haru wo yobou to
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.65,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Ono utsu hibiki michi hiraku utagoe
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kodama ga mune ni hazunde kuru no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kono oosora no niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-Japanese,,0,0,0,,Kibou ni todoku niji ni naritai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.59,0:00:29.77,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow I made on that starry night
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.02,0:00:36.70,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To not let this flame die
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.98,0:00:47.83,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I won't forget the vow made on that brilliant red morning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.08,0:00:56.76,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,To call out for spring, dyed with young leaves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.04,0:01:08.65,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,Cutting axes open up roads, under the sound of singing
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.93,0:01:20.54,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,The echoes bounce around in my chest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.82,0:01:26.38,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow in this big sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.66,0:01:36.18,Lucy-Song-English,,0,0,0,,I want to be a rainbow that reaches out to hope
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.85,0:01:47.70,Lucy-Ep-Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,306.667)\fade(337,259)}Ep. 16 - The Boozed Doctor
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.88,0:01:59.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Me and Lucy-May went to the forest\Na bit further away from our home
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:02.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,to gather some dead twigs\Nthat we'll make into firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.87,0:02:09.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my? Isn't it a koala?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.16,0:02:25.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh. It's no use. Climbing somewhere\Nthat high is out of my reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.80,0:02:35.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Lucy-May even remembers\Nshe's supposed to be gathering branches.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.39,0:02:39.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please climb down, little koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.69,0:02:44.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're not koala!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.19,0:02:48.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Something like a fox!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.21,0:02:51.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.19,0:02:55.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you wanna climb up there\Nto break the branches from the tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.15,0:02:56.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look over there, sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:02:57.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.70,0:03:00.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:05.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw it, I thought\Nit was a koala. But it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.60,0:03:07.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's looking at us, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.56,0:03:09.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It has a pretty little face, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.11,0:03:11.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of animal could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.31,0:03:13.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna catch it, sis.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.18,0:03:17.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well feel free to catch it,\Nif you can climb this tree.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I can't climb it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.39,0:03:20.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't nothing we can do, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.68,0:03:23.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You go catch it, instead!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not right in the head, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:30.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. There's no way\Nyou can climb up there either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.14,0:03:33.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you know, just give up\Nand gather some firewood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.09,0:03:44.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Did you see? Sis, did you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.41,0:03:48.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a baby! A baby is clinging onto her back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.38,0:03:56.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Wow! I so wanna\Nhave it as a pet! It's adorable!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Australia sure is full\Nof tree-perching creatures, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:18.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to start learning\Ntree-climbing starting today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:25.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The animal we saw\Nresembled a possum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.96,0:04:29.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As we would learn later, it was a species\Ncalled common brushtail possum.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.28,0:04:40.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That thing is heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:41.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We overloaded it a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:42.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe dump it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:47.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Dad said to get enough\Nto sustain an open fire for a long while.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.21,0:04:48.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.22,0:04:52.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They're charring the tips of the wood that'd they make into the pillars, though I don't know why.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:57.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's Billy over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:58.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.50,0:05:00.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, we can have him pull this for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.80,0:05:04.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Or even have him capture that animal\Nwe saw perched on the tree for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.10,0:05:06.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that!\NWhat are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.38,0:05:09.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta take this firewood\Nto father quickly, or else...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.53,0:05:11.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it shouldn't take all that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.60,0:05:12.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Not now, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ya finished gathering it already?\N'Twas fast, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.09,0:05:18.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it still weighs a ton.\NCare to help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.39,0:05:20.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure. 'Course. That's why I came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.62,0:05:22.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Because I'm the one strong here, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.08,0:05:24.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You'd help us a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.11,0:05:26.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just leave it to me, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.79,0:05:30.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.91,0:05:35.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Told you it's heavy.\NLucy-May, let's push too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.50,0:05:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucy-May,\Nthat's not necessary at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.84,0:05:40.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't really been\Nputting my spine into pulling now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:42.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.03,0:05:45.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.32,0:05:51.25,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.25,0:05:53.87,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't seem like you're really\Nall that strong, Billy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.90,0:05:55.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May, let's both push from behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.68,0:05:56.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.59,0:05:58.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Billy, we're pushing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.26,0:05:59.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:01.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.51,0:06:12.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If ya ever need to carry something even heavier,\Nain't no way it budges without a cart underneath.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.43,0:06:15.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, Billy, what brings you here, actually?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:18.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I was at your house,\Ncause my dad also went there.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:23.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My! Does that mean your old man is gonna\Nlend us a hand with rebuilding our shack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.19,0:06:26.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly! He already refused to go\Nto Mr. Pettywell's site.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:28.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I bet Mr. Pettywell was fuming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.24,0:06:31.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Was so mad his face went all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.70,0:06:37.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, everyone.\NGood job, good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.00,0:06:41.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off to find a replacement for Mr. Jamling.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.73,0:06:46.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, please continue with the construction\Nin accordance with this blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:50.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.90,0:06:56.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.70,0:07:08.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By sawing all the pieces in advance like this,\Nwe expedite the final assembly, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:09.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.40,0:07:14.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The prefabricated home that we sold to Mr. Pettywell\Nwas also made with that consideration in mind, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.08,0:07:18.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,All the parts of the house are sawed\Nin advance and mapped on the blueprint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.00,0:07:20.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly so.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:29.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jamling, even though you've left, they still can\Nconstruct that prefabricated house somehow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:32.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,They definitely can,\Nif they take their time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.40,0:07:35.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But truth be told, none of them except me\Nseems to know what he's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.51,0:07:39.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can imagine Mr. Pettiwell's angry face now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.51,0:07:40.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ben, let's continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.74,0:07:41.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.47,0:07:49.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aight. The tea was delicious.\NThanks a bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:52.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't help noticing\Nyou don't drink any alcohol these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.31,0:07:56.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alas, there ain't none within reach,\N'sides, I've been somewhat broke lately anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.92,0:07:59.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If only you had plenty of patients to examine...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.80,0:08:00.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.62,0:08:03.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I know! You should put out a signboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.10,0:08:05.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Signboard, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.00,0:08:10.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aight. I'll go get a fitting piece of wood, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:18.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doc, you need something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Ah, no-no.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.79,0:08:22.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Jamling, has your leg healed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.18,0:08:27.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, thanks to you, it's fine,\Nwith just a slight limp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.57,0:08:29.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ain't that dandy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.32,0:08:32.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, you plan to use\Nthat plank for somethin'?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.20,0:08:34.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,This one? Yes, we'll use it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:35.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I see.
Comment: 0,0:08:35.99,0:08:36.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.61,0:08:41.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Popple, about this plank...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.69,0:08:43.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly, we're using that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.47,0:08:46.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, why do you require a piece of wood?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.58,0:08:50.94,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's nothin'. Was jus' thinking\Nof making a little signboard.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.29,0:08:56.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please, Billy! Come to those woods with me\Nonce we're done with this, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see why I should.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.01,0:09:01.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's 'cause Billy is such an unparalleled\Ntree-climbing pro!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:03.85,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Coaxing ain't gonna get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:07.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Fine. As long as you agree\Nto go there with me, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why is it that the lumber\Nwon't rot if we char it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.61,0:09:32.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:35.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How come the lumber doesn't rot\Nif we treat it with fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.90,0:09:37.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:41.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... It's been this way for eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:42.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:53.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aight, let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:55.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Should be ready by now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.48,0:09:59.52,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, this would do.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.20,0:10:03.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, what are you doing with it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.07,0:10:04.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, look here to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.89,0:10:13.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my. That's your signboard, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.89,0:10:14.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.89,0:10:20.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where will you post it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.42,0:10:21.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,How about on the tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.93,0:10:23.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.08,0:10:25.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be too far away from the road\Nfor anyone to read it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:28.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Methinks you oughta post it\Nsomewhere near the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.33,0:10:30.02,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.40,0:10:31.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.08,0:10:34.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! How about you nail it to the tree over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.83,0:10:35.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.48,0:10:39.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.17,0:10:42.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute, though.\NIt would need this to hang there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.88,0:11:04.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then. Time for a doctor's visit\Nto our neighbor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.02,0:11:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:09.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you told\Nnot to get your eyes off the fire?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.77,0:11:12.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Oh no! It slipped my mind completely!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.59,0:11:16.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Lucy-May.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.39,0:11:17.41,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.42,0:11:18.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind, c'mere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:30.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So big now, ain't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.73,0:11:31.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And cute, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.85,0:11:36.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's cute, but three baby goats\Nwill make the milk run low.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.10,0:11:37.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's not the case!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.60,0:11:40.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone of us gets to drink\Na cup of milk every morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.92,0:11:44.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But suppose she only had one baby,\Nshe would produce more milk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.19,0:11:46.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:49.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Billy, what are you trying to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.38,0:11:53.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you wanted me to follow you\Ninto those woods, dincha?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.97,0:11:57.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's correct. It's to catch\Nthe animal we saw there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.69,0:12:02.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I feel there are plenty more\Nof different animals over there, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.12,0:12:04.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning, I'd need to climb a tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.31,0:12:07.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally! You can't catch it any other way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.18,0:12:09.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I wanna have a goat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.00,0:12:10.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You don't need all tree baby goats, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.31,0:12:16.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! I see, so that's what it all was about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.99,0:12:21.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Lucy-May: you found this goat,\Nso you're also the one to let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.10,0:12:27.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Think I need to ask grown-ups in the house\Nif we can give it to someone else or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:29.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then you don't mind me having it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.58,0:12:30.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:33.16,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you manage\Nto catch that creature we saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:35.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I will definitely catch it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.88,0:12:38.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I also feel like there should be koalas there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.11,0:12:40.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Gonna catch 'em all!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When you do, I'll give you\Nthe second baby goat, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.41,0:12:44.34,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.36,0:12:45.36,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.24,0:12:47.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.26,0:12:47.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,'Course.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.40,0:12:51.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's almost my turn\Nto watch the fire instead of Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.97,0:12:55.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But you've not been commanded\Nto do anything yet, innit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.97,0:13:00.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go then, but quietly.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:12.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody has got a clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.54,0:13:13.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's a success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.66,0:13:14.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,A great success!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:32.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,On which tree did you see it, exactly?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.61,0:13:34.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was around here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.39,0:13:36.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! There's that tree!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.95,0:13:37.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.89,0:13:42.57,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Can you still see that animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.59,0:13:43.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I don't see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And the greenery sure is thick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.59,0:13:49.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I first saw it sitting low,\Nbut then it climbed higher.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.45,0:13:50.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's one tall tree, y'know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.39,0:13:53.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Climb it, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.59,0:13:56.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Want me to climb it\Nwithout even knowing for sure it's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.83,0:13:59.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It definitely {\i1}was{\i0} there before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.30,0:14:01.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well a lot of time had passed since then.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.71,0:14:03.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't it have left by now?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.20,0:14:05.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You climb to check it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.49,0:14:10.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... Hm. Sure is a tall one...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it, Billy!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.58,0:14:25.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Kate, where's Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:27.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,She was around here up until a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.19,0:14:31.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Lucy-May! Lucy-May?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.19,0:14:34.07,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, there's no helping it.\NLet's just bring him along.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.09,0:14:35.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But the riverbank is full of dangers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.93,0:14:37.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, we could probably ask Kate to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:39.32,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You're probably right. Kate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.51,0:14:40.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:45.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look after Tob. Me and mom\Nare going to the river to do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.39,0:14:47.95,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But it's my turn to watch the fire...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.95,0:14:48.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,We know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.87,0:14:51.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But there's no way we can\Nbring Tob along to the riverside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.73,0:14:55.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When we're doing the laundry,\Nwe won't be able to keep an eye on Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, alright.\NI'll look after him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.54,0:15:02.84,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Tob, go play some with your sister Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.79,0:15:06.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't really play with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.82,0:15:09.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry. Then, you just keep each other company.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.92,0:15:12.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And let's hope Lucy-May returns some time soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.27,0:15:14.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then, feel free to entrust Tob to her, Kate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.59,0:15:15.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.02,0:15:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And here...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.49,0:15:39.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It's not here, Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.51,0:15:41.63,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think did it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.63,0:15:44.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It could have moved\Nto any other tree around here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.46,0:15:47.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:50.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So? D'you notice it on any other tree?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.88,0:15:52.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.29,0:15:53.22,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.38,0:15:59.54,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Look out! Stop there, Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.99,0:16:01.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Billy?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:04.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,There's a snake! Right behind you! Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.89,0:16:07.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.40,0:16:12.70,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It might be a poisonous species!\NRun, Lucy-May!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.81,0:16:17.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Dashing away is also dangerous!\NIt may then spring at me in a flash!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:21.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then just stay where you are,\Nwhile I climb down to try to kill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:25.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Lucy-May! Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.90,0:16:50.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That's one incredible bird.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.98,0:16:52.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of bird could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.57,0:16:57.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go back, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.69,0:16:58.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, you go home first\Nwith what's already in that basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.84,0:17:08.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do the rest of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.49,0:17:11.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll probably do just that.\NSorting out the dinner is also on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.98,0:17:13.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Counting on you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, our esteemed neighbor is also here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:17.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.59,0:17:22.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, it's a perfect day for laundry, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.30,0:17:23.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.29,0:17:24.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.15,0:17:25.45,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Clara.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:27.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is your husband feeling any better?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.31,0:17:28.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for asking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:31.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,It seems the fever had subsided\Nand he's finally regaining his strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.90,0:17:34.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton saw him just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.12,0:17:36.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He said there's no longer anything to worry about.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.51,0:17:37.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,When I first saw him,\Nhe didn't seem all that reliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.69,0:17:43.58,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But Doctor Deighton has proven himself\Nan excellent physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.58,0:17:45.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if you say so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:47.33,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Am I mistaken?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.33,0:17:50.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? No, that's not what I meant to say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.61,0:17:53.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Just that the Doctor is a terrible drunkard.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.22,0:17:56.15,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But he had to refrain from it\Nfor the last two or three days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.15,0:17:57.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:18:01.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My husband is recovering at a lightning speed,\Nand I felt like celebrating it...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:06.35,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So I encouraged the Doctor\Nto have some of our whiskey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.37,0:18:07.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Then the Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:10.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He drank several glasses\Nbecause it was so delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.60,0:18:13.05,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Several glasses?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:23.08,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling!
Comment: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:23.92,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.93,0:18:25.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Come here! Quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.30,0:18:34.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... So it was here, after all.\NDoctor Deighton's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:38.37,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, thank goodness. The rumors of a doctor\Nstarting a practice in the area were true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.38,0:18:40.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The sign points over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.50,0:18:48.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:51.73,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,G'day!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.30,0:18:53.80,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,May I help you with something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.99,0:18:57.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Young miss, is there any doctor around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.31,0:18:58.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, there is one.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.26,0:18:59.78,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But inside here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.00,0:19:01.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This boy is sick, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:04.28,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed he is. That's why we need the doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:07.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, he went to our neighbor's, Mrs. Mac's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:08.72,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,He has a patient there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.73,0:19:10.62,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Which means he'll be back in no time, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.21,0:19:12.13,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.58,0:19:13.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.08,0:19:16.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go invite him here for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.01,0:19:19.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Good. You'd help us a great deal if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.04,0:19:20.49,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I can do it, no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.50,0:19:22.98,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Feel free to rest here while you wait, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to trouble you...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.79,0:19:27.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to Mrs. Mac's for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.90,0:19:30.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,And you stay here\Nwithout roaming around, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.62,0:19:32.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.59,0:19:45.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Darling, he'll be alright, won't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.90,0:19:48.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Consider him safe already.\NThe doctor will see him in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.30,0:19:50.99,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, but this fever is terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.13,0:20:02.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My bag! Bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.82,0:20:04.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I have it here, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.74,0:20:08.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hic... Aye, much obliged, lil' miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:12.50,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The patient is a little boy\Nabout the same age as our Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.51,0:20:15.31,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,His dad and mom seem morbidly worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.32,0:20:17.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please hurry up to examine him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.02,0:20:18.65,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I got it, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.66,0:20:20.00,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's rush there if so!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.00,0:20:22.10,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Hey, I can't run.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.11,0:20:27.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nah... Out of question. Look! I'm trying.\NThere, there, there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.58,0:20:29.47,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.48,0:20:31.60,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Deighton,\Nare you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.61,0:20:33.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... My bad, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.79,0:20:35.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I just tripped over a tree root.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.98,0:20:37.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do alright this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.32,0:20:39.55,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.55,0:20:40.93,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.93,0:20:43.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Nah... I'm good, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.09,0:20:45.14,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, can go now. Let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.79,0:20:49.81,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Like this! Like this. Like like like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.98,0:20:51.86,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, let's just walk slowly for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.09,0:20:53.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.01,0:20:56.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.02,0:20:58.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If we walk, it shouldn't take that long.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.60,0:21:01.42,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you need to get so drunk, Doc?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:05.90,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Well I never thought I may have another patient\Ncoming to me as soon as today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.95,0:21:06.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.99,0:21:08.21,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:10.66,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.69,0:21:11.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.79,0:21:12.79,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,The bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.37,0:21:18.17,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you just now that I have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:19.01,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.10,0:21:21.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's good. Good, good, very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.38,0:21:28.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,G'day, ma'am.\NWhere's that poor fellow feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.72,0:21:29.88,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.39,0:21:33.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.13,0:21:35.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. Howdy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.40,0:21:37.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the sick man?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.78,0:21:39.48,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, it's this child.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.50,0:21:42.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, you go lay him right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.29,0:21:45.68,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. Need you to step aside a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.69,0:21:46.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:48.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I can't cure him by just looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.59,0:21:51.83,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I beg your pardon.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.61,0:21:53.61,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.01,0:22:00.71,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? That looks pretty constipated to me.\NGotta give him an enema now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.72,0:22:02.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Glycerin, glycerin...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.40,0:22:04.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, your bag is over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.31,0:22:06.11,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yes, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.20,0:22:10.39,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see, here we got...\NWhat's this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.39,0:22:14.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.68,0:22:16.51,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, can you come out for a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.53,0:22:19.69,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but right now I'm examining this kid, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.69,0:22:22.97,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I know you do! That's exactly why\NI want you to come here for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.05,0:22:26.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? My, my, what could be the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.23,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,So what in the world was it\Nthat you wanted, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.24,0:22:33.24,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Please shut your eyes for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:36.03,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to alleviate your intoxication now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:38.67,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? No, I appreciate the offer, but what're you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.69,0:22:39.91,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.91,0:22:40.59,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.95,0:22:49.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! That's cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.89,0:22:53.40,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am, what was that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.42,0:22:55.19,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,If that didn't help, I can do one more.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.20,0:22:58.06,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,No-no-no! I'm sober enough already. Really sober!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.07,0:23:00.82,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,That kid is about the same age as our Tob.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.83,0:23:03.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, please do whatever it takes to help him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.44,0:23:09.26,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Got it, I'll make every effort. That's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:14.30,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.32,0:23:17.38,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, nothing to worry about.\NI'm no longer drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.39,0:23:19.12,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Now, first things first.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.12,0:23:22.64,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, this constipation in the bowels\Nis unmistakable.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.64,0:23:24.53,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start with an enema.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.09,0:23:34.96,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Is Doctor Deighton managing it well?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.99,0:23:36.43,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's all well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.85,0:23:43.74,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mom really surprised us when she doused\NDoctor Deighton with water.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.89,0:23:48.29,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,But if she hadn't done it,\NDoctor would probably still be dead drunk.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.09,0:23:53.20,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Very soon, the sick boy also got better.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.28,0:24:08.09,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Pettywell's black dog\Ngot one of our baby goats.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.11,0:24:10.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,You can't die! No way you die!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.79,0:24:14.76,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Next on Lucy-May of the Southern Rainbow:\N"A Tragic Incident".
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.77,0:24:15.89,Lucy-Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!
